{"id": "1444694889223688294", "channel_id": "1444694889223688294", "type": 0, "author_id": "1302298693369856000", "author_name": "flim_of_life_burst", "author_bot": false, "content": "✡️在此，我向你允諾，高塔投下的陰影終將吞噬世界。\n    \n被異維接納的神子，亦是暴君最忠實的擁躉。從未失手、從不動搖、從無憐憫——沒有任何人能夠逃脫這場名為“終末”的狩獵。\n\n*UID：100251655\n*立繪：米畫師_南方度假皮皮（已取得商用及二改授權）\n*更多信息請見圖片\n*wiki網頁：https://morimens.huijiwiki.com/wiki/%E5%BC%82%E5%BA%A6%C2%B7%E7%B4%A2%E7%93%A6%E5%B0%94%E6%A0%BC", "timestamp": "2025-11-30T14:21:42.724000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-11-30T19:16:18.971000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 11}], "attachments": [{"id": "1444694890226122842", "filename": "IMG_2640.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 3360347, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1444694889223688294/1444694890226122842/IMG_2640.png?ex=69cbd876&is=69ca86f6&hm=61b8a96597192c5a811643b9b1088c70e66bcf204ba8f3030080ec1fd3b3e753&"}, {"id": "1444694890847141990", "filename": "IMG_7553.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 442171, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1444694889223688294/1444694890847141990/IMG_7553.jpg?ex=69cbd877&is=69ca86f7&hm=bfd1385d5d4ab2c1e4b3d21a23204e9a112a7328adb36c50dcc49257595c1a08&"}, {"id": "1444694891279024272", "filename": "IMG_7606.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 670470, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1444694889223688294/1444694891279024272/IMG_7606.jpg?ex=69cbd877&is=69ca86f7&hm=7dfc74d89a2d7472f9bc3cd0d682e7ce67e01285417181f0a57b89a98237e87e&"}, {"id": "1444694891794792509", "filename": "IMG_7951.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 980423, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1444694889223688294/1444694891794792509/IMG_7951.png?ex=69cbd877&is=69ca86f7&hm=d1a2df75abb44fe142d0ade3d335d0c31a6378015c7be1473c42f38f4415c747&"}, {"id": "1444694892210290738", "filename": "IMG_7950.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 966965, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/atta